单变量离群点检测

boxplot.stats() 函数将返回生成盒图过程中产生的统计值，其中有一个 out 分量，是一个离群点的 list 。

library(ggplot2)
set.seed(3147)
x <- rnorm(100)
summary(x)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
## -3.3150 -0.4837  0.1867  0.1098  0.7120  2.6860
boxplot.stats(x)$out
## [1] -3.315391  2.685922 -3.055717  2.571203
pltbase <- qplot(seq_along(x), x)

boxplot(x)

多变量：

y <- rnorm(100)
df <- data.frame(x, y)
rm(x, y)
head(df)
##             x          y
## 1 -3.31539150  0.7619774
## 2 -0.04765067 -0.6404403
## 3  0.69720806  0.7645655
## 4  0.35979073  0.3131930
## 5  0.18644193  0.1709528
## 6  0.27493834 -0.8441813
attach(df)
(a <- which(x %in% boxplot.stats(x)$out))
## [1]  1 33 64 74
(b <- which(y %in% boxplot.stats(y)$out))
## [1] 24 25 49 64 74
detach(df)
(outlier.list1 <- intersect(a,b))
## [1] 64 74
plot(df)
points(df[outlier.list1,], col="red", pch="+", cex=2.5)

# 选择x，y的所有离群点作为二者的离群点
(outlier.list2 <- union(a,b))
## [1]  1 33 64 74 24 25 49
plot(df)
points(df[outlier.list2,], col="blue", pch="x", cex=2)

LOF 离群检测

LOF(Local Outlier Factor) 算法只作用于数值型数据。

With LOF, the local density of a point is compared with that of its neighbors. If the former is significantly lower than the latter (with an LOF value greater than one), the point is in a sparser region than its neighbors, which suggests it be an outlier.

plot_iris_outliers <- function(outlier.scores, data) {
  plot(density(outlier.scores))
  outliers <- order(outlier.scores, decreasing=T)[1:5]
  print(outliers)
  print(data[outliers,])
  
  n <- nrow(data)
  labels <- 1:n
  labels[-outliers] <- "."
  biplot(prcomp(data), cex=.8, xlabs=labels)

  pch <- rep(".", n)
  pch[outliers] <- "+"
  col <- rep("black", n)
  col[outliers] <- "red"
  pairs(data, pch=pch, col=col)
}

library(DMwR)
iris2 <- iris[,-5]
outlier.scores <- lofactor(iris2, k=5)
plot_iris_outliers(outlier.scores, iris2)

## [1]  42 107  23 110  63
##     Sepal.Length Sepal.Width Petal.Length Petal.Width
## 42           4.5         2.3          1.3         0.3
## 107          4.9         2.5          4.5         1.7
## 23           4.6         3.6          1.0         0.2
## 110          7.2         3.6          6.1         2.5
## 63           6.0         2.2          4.0         1.0

Rlof 包提供了 lof 函数作为 LOF 算法的并行实现。

library(Rlof)
outlier.scores2 <- lof(iris2, k=5)
plot_iris_outliers(outlier.scores2, iris2)

## [1]  42 107  23 110  63
##     Sepal.Length Sepal.Width Petal.Length Petal.Width
## 42           4.5         2.3          1.3         0.3
## 107          4.9         2.5          4.5         1.7
## 23           4.6         3.6          1.0         0.2
## 110          7.2         3.6          6.1         2.5
## 63           6.0         2.2          4.0         1.0

outlier.scores3 <- lof(iris2, k=c(5:10))
plot_iris_outliers(outlier.scores3, iris2)

## [1]  42 192 342 492 642

通过聚类来实现的离群值检测

将数据归入不同的聚类，那些没有归入任何聚类的点就是离群值。

iris2 <- iris[,1:4]
kmeans.result <- kmeans(iris2, centers=3)
kmeans.result$centers
##   Sepal.Length Sepal.Width Petal.Length Petal.Width
## 1     6.850000    3.073684     5.742105    2.071053
## 2     5.901613    2.748387     4.393548    1.433871
## 3     5.006000    3.428000     1.462000    0.246000
kmeans.result$cluster
##   [1] 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3
##  [36] 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 2 2 1 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2
##  [71] 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 1 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 2 1 2 1 1 1
## [106] 1 2 1 1 1 1 1 1 2 2 1 1 1 1 2 1 2 1 2 1 1 2 2 1 1 1 1 1 2 1 1 1 1 2 1
## [141] 1 1 2 1 1 1 2 1 1 2
centers <- kmeans.result$centers[kmeans.result$cluster, ]
distances <- sqrt(rowSums((iris2 - centers)^2))
outliers <- order(distances, decreasing=T)[1:5]
print(outliers)
## [1]  99  58  94  61 119
print(iris2[outliers,])
##     Sepal.Length Sepal.Width Petal.Length Petal.Width
## 99           5.1         2.5          3.0         1.1
## 58           4.9         2.4          3.3         1.0
## 94           5.0         2.3          3.3         1.0
## 61           5.0         2.0          3.5         1.0
## 119          7.7         2.6          6.9         2.3
plot(iris2[,c("Sepal.Length", "Sepal.Width")], pch="o", col=kmeans.result$cluster, cex=0.3)
points(kmeans.result$centers[,c("Sepal.Length", "Sepal.Width")], col=1:3, pch=8, cex=1.5)
points(iris2[outliers, c("Sepal.Length", "Sepal.Width")], pch="+", col=4, cex=1.5)

时间序列的离群值检测

使用 stl 进行鲁棒回归解耦

str(AirPassengers)
##  Time-Series [1:144] from 1949 to 1961: 112 118 132 129 121 135 148 148 136 119 ...
f <- stl(AirPassengers, "periodic", robust=TRUE)
(outliers <- which(f$weights<1e-8))
##  [1]  79  91  92 102 103 104 114 115 116 126 127 128 138 139 140
op <- par(mar=c(0, 4, 0, 3), oma=c(5, 0, 4, 0), mfcol=c(4, 1))
plot(f, set.pars=NULL)
sts <- f$time.series
points(time(sts)[outliers], 0.8*sts[,"remainder"][outliers], pch="x", col="red")

par(op)
